{
  "title": "Smoky Dutch Eggplant Toast",
  "description": "A smoky and dense Dutch dish perfect for a lazy Sunday, featuring roasted eggplant, crispy toast, and a blend of vegetarian-friendly flavors. This hearty recipe is sure to satisfy your cravings.",
